
Types:
  individual
.

Pedestrian States:
  Scared
.

Selector:
  Type: individual
  Select: Everyone
.

Event:
  Name: Fire
  Start: 0 seconds after !Start
  Produce: Fire (Visual)
  Where: Random
.

Event:
  Name: Fire_Alarm
  Start: 15 seconds after !Fire
  Produce: Auditory
  Where: Everywhere
.

Action (individual):
  Stimulus: See !Fire, See #Scared, Hear !Fire_Alarm
  Response: scale velocity 2.0, be #Scared, set goal nearest exit
  Produce: 
.
